headline: Klarna Set to Report Q4 Earnings: Key Factors Investors Should Watch
summary: KLAR readies Q4 results with 18.5% revenue growth expected and GMV near $38B as consumer receivables are likely to have increased.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks to Own for Decades and 1 That Underwhelm
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
